    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits some fading and wear in high-traffic areas. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but potential buyers should be aware that it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at an accessible price point.",
