    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior to the spotless interior, offering a driving experience that feels brand new. Truly a rare find for the discerning buyer who wants the very best!",
